From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 01/10] nickel: branding — rename product to Nickel Browser

Replace all "Chromium" product identity with "Nickel Browser".
ungoogled-chromium has already stripped Google branding; this patch
applies the Nickel identity on top of that clean Chromium base.

Files changed:
  chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING
  chrome/installer/linux/common/chromium-browser/chromium-browser.info

The BRANDING file drives the product name used throughout the build
(window title, about page, desktop entry, etc.).
---
 chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING | 12 +++---
 chrome/installer/linux/common/chromium-browser/chromium-browser.info |  4 +-
 2 files changed, 8 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

diff --git a/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING b/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING
+++ b/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING
@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@
-COMPANY_FULLNAME=The Chromium Authors
-COMPANY_SHORTNAME=Chromium
-PRODUCT_FULLNAME=Chromium
-PRODUCT_SHORTNAME=Chromium
-PRODUCT_EXE=chromium
-PRODUCT_INSTALLER_FULLNAME=Chromium Installer
+COMPANY_FULLNAME=Nickel Browser Community
+COMPANY_SHORTNAME=Nickel
+PRODUCT_FULLNAME=Nickel Browser
+PRODUCT_SHORTNAME=Nickel
+PRODUCT_EXE=nickel-browser
+PRODUCT_INSTALLER_FULLNAME=Nickel Browser Installer
diff --git a/chrome/installer/linux/common/chromium-browser/chromium-browser.info b/chrome/installer/linux/common/chromium-browser/chromium-browser.info
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/chrome/installer/linux/common/chromium-browser/chromium-browser.info
+++ b/chrome/installer/linux/common/chromium-browser/chromium-browser.info
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-[Desktop Entry]
-Name=Chromium Web Browser
-Comment=Access the Internet
-Icon=chromium-browser
+[Desktop Entry]
+Name=Nickel Browser
+Comment=Block Everything. Leak Nothing. Own Your Web.
+Icon=nickel-browser
-- 
2.40.0
